Ref: When you pass the logical ID of this resource to the intrinsic Ref function, Ref returns the ARN, such as arn:aws:pcs:us-east-1:111122223333:cluster/pcs_hta14wrehh/queue/pcs_nhrw94erov.

GetAtt.Description: The unique Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the queue.
The list of errors that occurred during queue provisioning.
The generated unique ID of the queue.
The provisioning status of the queue. The provisioning status doesn't indicate the overall health of the queue.
